Content:

A Hip-Hop/Trip-Hop compilation from mainland China

The title of the CD in pinyin is:  liao yuan xing huo VOL.3 bian shuo bian chang

-A literal translation word-by-word would be:  
--"burn plains star fire VOL.3 side to say side to sing"

-even closer would be:
--"burn plains spark VOL.3 talking and singing"

But, you can&#039;t always translate chinese into english strictly word for word.

-My translation would be something like:
